ata set, the model found 32 additional (i.e., not included in\nthe benchmark data set) known pulsars, and several potential discoveries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Jul 2018 21:32:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Aug 2018 00:52:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-07"}
