ined. Similar strategies\nwill also allow the reach for generic boosted resonances searches in hadronic\nchannels to be extended.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Jul 2018 14:12:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Aug 2018 15:34:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 8 Feb 2019 07:44:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-11"}
